summary: Learn about .CEDPRJ files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: CEDPRJ files can be used for saving designs of CD, DVD, and Blu-ray disc labels, as well as DVD cases, DVD booklets, slim cases, jewel cases, and Blu-ray cases.

description: Disc cover project created by CoverEditor, a disc case design program included with Ashampoo Burning Studio; contains design information for print a disc label; allows users to save disc designs for later editing and printing.
